<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.5.8">
<l>uṟavātu milaḷeṉṟeṉ ṟoḻiyātu palarēcu malarā yiṟṟāl</l>
<l>maṟavātē yeppoḻutum māyavaṉē mātavaṉē yeṉkiṉ ṟaḷāl</l>
<l>piṟavāta pērāḷaṉ peṇṇāḷaṉ maṇṇāḷaṉ viṇṇōr taṅkaḷ</l>
<l>aṟavāḷa ṉeṉmakaḷaic ceytaṉaka ḷammaṉaimī raṟiki lēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The gossip with which many reproach [her], saying again and again</l>
<l rend="indent">that she does not have any relations, has truly become incessant;</l>
<l>Positively without fail, she always says, “Māyavaṉ, Mādhava.”</l>
<l>The great ruler who is without birth, ruler of the lady, ruler of earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">virtuous ruler of the celestials,</l>
<l>Ladies, I cannot understand what [he] did to my daughter.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
